data.description: Come on home to this warm, well-maintained turnkey 3-bedroom ranch on a full 2.2 acres in beautiful Palmyra! You can see true pride in ownership with updates inside and out. Stretch out in the added 347 square feet: there's 224 additional square feet in the added walkout bedroom and 123 square feet in the four-season room that opens right into the dining room. You can even turn this back into a 4-bedroom by adding a wall in the master! All maintenance has been completed - including fresh paint and carpeting, new vinyl siding, a 50-year metal roof and vinyl windows throughout - all installed in 2020! The electric panel was updated just 3 years ago. On top of that, you can cozy up to a 3-car heated garage with 2 main bays and one individual bay - ready to keep your cars happy! Reviewing offers Monday 3/8/2021 at 5:00 pm.
